594
00:52:32,320 --> 00:52:35,460
He gave me your address so I can bring you, too.

595
00:52:36,950 --> 00:52:39,720
Wait here. I'll call him for a second.

596
00:52:39,720 --> 00:52:41,320
Why?

597
00:52:42,120 --> 00:52:45,780
Will you tell him we had a falling out?

598
00:52:47,640 --> 00:52:50,300
