599
00:52:50,300 --> 00:52:52,960
That's what you hate the most.

600
00:52:54,420 --> 00:52:56,970
Disappointing your father.

601
00:53:06,080 --> 00:53:08,280
It's been so long, Jae Won.

602
00:53:08,280 --> 00:53:11,390
I'm sorry. I should've visited you more often.

603
00:53:11,390 --> 00:53:15,230
It's okay. We know how busy you are.

604
00:53:15,230 --> 00:53:16,480
Where's Mr. Kwon?

605
00:53:16,480 --> 00:53:19,620
He said he's almost here.

606
00:53:19,620 --> 00:53:21,190
Honey.

607
00:53:23,430 --> 00:53:26,440
I'm sorry. Am I too late?

608
00:53:28,400 --> 00:53:32,150
CEO Seo. Have a seat.

609
00:53:45,740 --> 00:53:49,860
Dean Choi said she could look forward to being hired

610
00:53:49,860 --> 00:53:52,790
as a full-time professor this time.

611
00:53:52,790 --> 00:53:55,640
Dean Choi from Yun Jin's school?

612
00:53:55,640 --> 00:53:57,480
It must've been difficult persuading him.

613
00:53:57,480 --> 00:54:00,110
Yun Jin has been an assistant professor for a long time.

614
00:54:00,770 --> 00:54:03,180
Gosh, that's so wonderful.

615
00:54:03,180 --> 00:54:05,590
Aren't you helping her too much?

616
00:54:05,590 --> 00:54:08,770
Does she even deserve it?

617
00:54:08,770 --> 00:54:11,220
Gosh, come on, Honey.

618
00:54:11,890 --> 00:54:14,090
You did the same for me.

619
00:54:14,090 --> 00:54:16,440
When I was in middle school,

620
00:54:17,140 --> 00:54:22,450
you had faith in me, supported me, and invested in me.

621
00:54:22,450 --> 00:54:24,450
It's for the same reason.

622
00:54:26,560 --> 00:54:28,920
The same reason?

623
00:54:30,030 --> 00:54:32,520
Is she holding something over your head?

624
00:54:32,520 --> 00:54:33,910
Pardon?

625
00:54:37,310 --> 00:54:39,680
I'm kidding. I'm kidding.

626
00:54:40,700 --> 00:54:45,840
I loved the look in your eyes then.

627
00:54:47,370 --> 00:54:49,520
Shouldn't we get a bottle of champagne?

628
