 I don't know. I don't even remember.

643
00:56:22,590 --> 00:56:25,630
 I haven't talked to him since I was 13, when my parents divorced.

644
00:56:25,630 --> 00:56:27,910
 It's been 30 years since I talked to him.

645
00:56:27,910 --> 00:56:31,640
So, where's Mr. Heo right now?

646
00:56:31,640 --> 00:56:34,380
He passed away last year.

647
